  <title>Gio.FILE_ATTRIBUTE_MOUNTABLE_IS_MEDIA_CHECK_AUTOMATIC</title>
  <p>A key in the "mountable" namespace for checking if a file (of type G_FILE_TYPE_MOUNTABLE)
is automatically polled for media.
Corresponding <link xref="Gio.FileAttributeType"/> is <link xref="Gio.FileAttributeType"/>.boolean.</p>
  <p>Since 2.22</p>
